@slow
Feature: Error Handling
    If something goes wrong, human-readable error messages are shown


Scenario: Task Does Not Exist (http 404)
    WHEN user opens the Task Manager with task "non-existing" preselected
    THEN an error "Aufgabe 'non-existing' existiert nicht." is shown


Scenario: Race Condition While Proceeding (500)
    GIVEN a task with OLC exists
    WHEN user opens the Task Manager
        AND user clicks the task's proceed cell
        AND another user completes the task
        AND user completes the task from the open proceed cell
    THEN the task is shown
        # no target status is "... eine Statuswechsel vorzunehmen."
        AND an error "Die Statusänderung ist nicht möglich." is shown
